Light Up 12 oz Drinking Cups - Blue - 1/pkg

Amaze your guests and pour them a drink in these colorful and bright 12 oz drinking cup. These illuminating cups will
column4: >awe your party guests as they quench their thirst
column5:
everyone will want to sip all their drinks from a glowing drinking glass.

Don't worry, it's plastic, so it won't break! However, you will need to snap the cup in a few places and give it a few shakes to allow the glow to start flowing.

column1:
Serve your drinks in these red, blue, or green glow-in-the-dark at any luau, birthday party, fiesta, barbecue, or any other special event held indoors or outdoors.

Choose any color and start pouring drinks into your own glowing drinking glass.
